  "translations": {
    "en": "Then the Originator would not be distinguished from the originated, nor the Powerful from the one over whom power is exercised, nor the Creator from the created. Exalted is Allah above this speech, an immense exaltation. Rather, He is the Creator of things not out of need. So when He created not out of need, limitation and modality are impossible regarding Him. So understand, if Allah the Exalted wills.'",
